  "story": "A deeply personal bhajan declaring Jesus as the one true Saviour. This traditional hymn has been a cornerstone of Hindi Christian worship, expressing the believer's complete trust in Christ. Its simple melody and heartfelt confession have strengthened the faith of generations across North India.",
